##Making peace with yourself does not mean compromising with the world

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

February 22,2020.

The 29th day of the 1st Lunar Month.

Wuhan closed for thirty-one.

The 30th day of the closing of the gate of Heaven.

I don't remember living with my family for so long after graduation, except for the heavy snow in 2008. Many in Florida, of course, feel as if they are living at home, giving themselves a long vacation and a chance to spend quality time with their families. Of course, I am also very grateful and cherish this time spent together treasure. Accompany her mother-in-law in the roof Sunning NA sole, once as if back to childhood. But apart from the occasional Suntan on the roof, a fixed time at a table to eat, I still spend most of the time alone. There was nothing more to talk about with the family other than the outbreak.

I think, in addition to the scars of the times and the generation gap between the elders, more of my own problems. Uncle Nagging me, through this time together, found that you are too casual, knowledge and action is not one. Wang Hao, my old live in friend, said the same thing about me: too self involved. Maybe that's why I've never been able to handle an intimate relationship. When does a person give up intimacy and run away from the world of social animals to live alone? I don't know.

One must learn to grow in relationships, to see one's needs, wants, hurts, and sins through intimacy, and not to place those parts of oneself in the hope of a partner to satisfy, but to learn how to heal and explore. The Jewish philosopher Martin Buber said, you have to start on your own. If you do not live deeply with positive love, if you do not reveal the meaning of life in your own way, then life will remain meaningless to you.
